name: AI Avatar #187
description:
Using an AI guided by a Human artist, this collection aims to achieve the pinnacle of Human Beauty in the form of a portrait. Far beyond what each could have individually achieved, these portraits feature breathtaking beauty and astonishing realism.

Just as each Human is unique, each portrait is unique will only be minted once. This allows them to be used as the owner’s avatar and profile picture in the coming dawn of the Metaverse. Exclusive special editions with unique characterization and backstories will also be dropped during special occasions.
